cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new method for one-shot learning using deep learning techniques, specifically variational autoencoders. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of prior knowledge and generalization learning, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper uses neural networks, which is a topic related to neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
